<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="el">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Street Legends GR</title>
    <!-- Εισαγωγή γραμματοσειράς και εικονιδίων -->
    <link href="https://googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cloudflare.com">
    
    <style>
        /* --- ΓΕΝΙΚΑ ΣΤΥΛ --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .gold-text {
            color: #c5a059;
        }
        .btn-gold {
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid #c5a059;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-gold:hover {
            background-color: #c5a059;
            color: #000;
        }

        /* --- NAVIGATION --- */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 5%;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.9), transparent);
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .logo {
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .logo span { color: #c5a059; }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .nav-links li:hover { color: #c5a059; cursor: pointer; }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            height: 95vh;
            /* Αντικατάστησε το URL με τη δική σου εικόνα αυτοκινήτων */
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.3), #050505), url('https://unsplash.com') center/cover no-repeat;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-left: 8%;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .hero .subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #ccc;
        }
        .meet-box {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            border-left: 3px solid #c5a059;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            max-width: 320px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .meet-box .title {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .meet-box .date {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* --- ΥΠΟΔΟΧΗ --- */
        .welcome-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .welcome-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .welcome-section p {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* --- ΧΑΡΑΚΤΗΡΙΣΤΙΚΑ (FEATURES) --- */
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 40px 5%;
        }
        .feature-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background: #0c0c0c;
            border-top: 3px solid #c5a059;
        }
        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #c5a059;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #777;
        }

        /* --- GALLERY & ΑΝΑΚΟΙΝΩΣΕΙΣ --- */
        .main-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 60px 5%;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .main-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
            height: 180px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .gallery-item .label {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 15px;
            left: 15px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .announcement-box {
            background: #0c0c0c;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        }
        .announcement-item {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .announcement-item h4 {
            color: #c5a059;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .announcement-item p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            background: #000;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #111;
        }
        footer h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .social-icons i:hover { color: #c5a059; cursor: pointer; }
        .instagram-tag {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAVIGATION -->
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">STREET LEGENDS <span>GR</span></div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li>ΑΡΧΙΚΗ</li>
            <li>ΣΥΝΑΝΤΗΣΕΙΣ & EVENTS</li>
            <li>GALLERY</li>
            <li>PROJECT CARS</li>
            <li>ΕΠΙΚΟΙΝΩΝΙΑ</li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <header class="hero">
        <h1>STREET<br><span class="gold-text">LEGENDS</span><br>GR</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">ΕΚΕΙ ΠΟΥ ΤΑ ΑΥΤΟΚΙΝΗΤΑ ΓΙΝΟΝΤΑΙ ΘΡΥΛΟΙ.</p>
        
        <div class="meet-box">
            <div class="title"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i> ΕΠΟΜΕΝΗ ΣΥΝΑΝΤΗΣΗ:</div>
            <div class="date">17/07/2026 - 18:00</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <a href="#" class="btn-gold">Δείτε περισσότερα <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right" style="font-size: 0.6rem;"></i></a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- WELCOME -->
    <section class="welcome-section">
        <h2>ΚΑΛΩΣ ΗΡΘΕΣ ΣΤΟ <span class="gold-text">STREET LEGENDS GR</span></h2>
        <p>Μια κοινότητα για όσους ζουν και αναπνέουν για τα αυτοκίνητα. Συναντήσεις, βόλτες, πάθος και αληθινές φιλίες.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- FEATURES -->
    <section class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i>
            <h3>ΚΟΙΝΟΤΗΤΑ</h3>
            <p>Γίνε μέλος μιας μεγάλης παρέας με το ίδιο πάθος.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-car"></i>
            <h3>ΣΥΝΑΝΤΗΣΕΙΣ</h3>
            <p>Διοργανώνουμε τακτικά meets και εκδηλώσεις.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-camera"></i>
            <h3>ΦΩΤΟΓΡΑΦΙΕΣ</h3>
            <p>Στιγμές από τις καλύτερες συναντήσεις μας.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-wrench"></i>
            <h3>PROJECT CARS</h3>
            <p>Παρουσίαση και εξέλιξη των αυτοκινήτων μας.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MAIN SECTION (GALLERY & ANNOUNCEMENTS) -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <!-- Gallery Preview -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">GALLERY PREVIEW</h2>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <!-- Αντικατάστησε τα URLs με δικές σου εικόνες -->
                <div class="gallery-item" style="background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('https://unsplash.com');">
                    <span class="gallery-label-box label">DRIFT</span>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item" style="background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('https://unsplash.com');">
                    <span class="label">JDM</span>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item" style="background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('https://unsplash.com');">
                    <span class="label">GERMAN STYLE</span>
